Company Overview of Inland Residential Properties Trust, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Inland Residential Properties Trust, Inc. acquires and manages a portfolio of multifamily properties in the United States. The company was formerly known as Inland Retail Properties Trust V, Inc. and changed its name to Inland Residential Properties Trust, Inc. in July 2014. Inland Residential Properties Trust, Inc. was founded in 2013 and is based in Oak Brook, Illinois.


2901 Butterfield RoadOak Brook, IL 60523United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 630-218-8000

www.inland-investments.com







